{
  "stem": "15115.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and then they took my father's yard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my father was-- was out of-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my oldest brother, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had quite a bit of money saved up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But since my-- my father was illiterate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was not educated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They never believed in banks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we had them all at home in paper, not in gold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If-- we weren't-- they weren't that smart to make the-- the-- the paper currency into gold.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then we would have been on top of the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they kept their old piles of big denominations of-- of-- of drachmas into the house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, when we used to go out in the evening, even before the war, my mother had to carry a-- a big bag of money with her when we'd go out for dinner, you know, because we didn't believe in banks.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you don't want to leave it at home, because they might rob you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my two brothers, they were-- and my-- my sister was younger, [? though. ?] My two brothers used to have apres-midis.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apres-midi is a French word, a Spanish word.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to get together at a house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they would-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would get a band and have a party at home, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd bring their own food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or they had their own clubs, the Jewish clubs, which we used to go-- boys and, you know-- and younger people of 20 to 18, 19, 20, 21.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to-- a lot of activities there, which I [INAUDIBLE] because I was young.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
